{"id": "EUVD-2025-31527", "enisaUuid": "220448c2-7c9e-3827-a8e2-0958420a39fb", "description": "In the Linux kernel, the following vulnerability has been resolved:\n\niommu/riscv: prevent NULL deref in iova_to_phys\n\nThe riscv_iommu_pte_fetch() function returns either NULL for\nunmapped/never-mapped iova, or a valid leaf pte pointer that\nrequires no further validation.\n\nriscv_iommu_iova_to_phys() failed to handle NULL returns.\nPrevent null pointer dereference in\nriscv_iommu_iova_to_phys(), and remove the pte validation.", "datePublished": "2025-09-05T18:31:27", "dateUpdated": "2025-11-25T21:32:04", "baseScore": 0.0, "references": ["https://git.kernel.org/stable/c/220c491490255b656672bb572b18460cd9155926", "https://git.kernel.org/stable/c/99d4d1a070870aa08163af8ce0522992b7f35d8c", "https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-39699"], "aliases": ["CVE-2025-39699"], "assigner": "Linux", "epss": 0.02, "enisaIdProduct": [{"id": "075574b4-5266-31c8-87ef-d24f7138d598", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "patch: 6.16.4"}, {"id": "0fc5b8df-a9e5-3019-a043-703fd8783d8a", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "488ffbf181718b9ad8c1838cb249d60973e78eda <220c491490255b656672bb572b18460cd9155926"}, {"id": "85ebe732-259a-3a34-b240-e919600fc66c", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "patch: 0"}, {"id": "8f5efd06-9dac-3133-84f3-cdc14ec736d7", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "488ffbf181718b9ad8c1838cb249d60973e78eda <99d4d1a070870aa08163af8ce0522992b7f35d8c"}, {"id": "8fcce479-1532-3503-9903-38663c3f184b", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "patch: 6.17"}, {"id": "dfc9b4e2-04ec-32bf-a1dc-f84efb216ed7", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "6.13"}], "enisaIdVendor": [{"id": "b88b7ac1-c692-338f-a75e-24aaf489dc58", "vendor": {"name": "Linux"}}], "isExploited": false}